<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q59_v5" title="Promedio_precipitaciones_inversion" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En cierta ciudad se registraron las precipitaciones de lluvia (en milímetros) de junio, julio, agosto y septiembre. Se sabe que el promedio de precipitaciones en esos cuatro meses fue de <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm. ¿Cuál de los siguientes posibles registros mensuales es coherente con ese promedio?</p>
    <div>Todos los valores indicados a continuación corresponden a precipitaciones mensuales en milímetros (mm).</div>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math> mm</p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La suma de estos cuatro valores es <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>130</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces el promedio es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>130</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> mm, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>32,5</m:mn></m:math> mm, y no <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math> mm</p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La suma de estos cuatro valores es <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>. Al dividir por <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>140</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, por lo tanto este registro sí es coherente con el promedio dado.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> mm</p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La suma de estos cuatro valores es <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces el promedio es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>125</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> mm, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>31,25</m:mn></m:math> mm, y no <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>55</m:mn></m:math> mm</p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La suma de estos cuatro valores es <m:math><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>55</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>160</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces el promedio es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> mm, y no <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: cálculo del promedio</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Usar la definición de promedio</strong></p>
            <p>Si el promedio de cuatro meses es <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, entonces la suma total de precipitaciones debe ser <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math> mm.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Revisar cada alternativa</strong></p>
            <p><em>Opción A:</em> <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>130</m:mn></m:math>. No sirve, porque la suma no es <m:math><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p><em>Opción B:</em> <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>. Sí sirve, porque la suma coincide con <m:math><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p><em>Opción C:</em> <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn></m:math>. No sirve, porque la suma no es <m:math><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p><em>Opción D:</em> <m:math><m:mn>25</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>55</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>160</m:mn></m:math>. No sirve, porque la suma no es <m:math><m:mn>140</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar el promedio de la opción correcta</strong></p>
            <p>En la opción B, el promedio es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>140</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El único registro mensual coherente con un promedio de <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm es la <strong>opción B</strong>: <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>35</m:mn></m:math> mm, <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math> mm y <m:math><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math> mm.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>